snippet.title: Castlevania Chronicles III   Dracula's Curse teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Warmachine Studios is BACK!  
I hope you all enjoy this short teaser trailer for my upcoming Castlevania 3 remake; Castlevania Chronicles 3 - Dracula's Curse!
I made this 10 years ago when i was still learning, and as most that remember would know, it was full of issues.  Not now!
More details to come in the following months.  Make sure to subscribe and stay up to date with all the news!
Consider joining the discord and meet some good folks as well!
https://discord.gg/3HjJcWzdea
